  "gwSpecs": {
    "description": "The Eliminator Lighting Stryker Wash is a 228W professional moving head wash featuring nineteen 12W 4-IN-1 (RGBW) LEDs, and motorized zoom (6 ~ 50-degrees) that allows the versatility to use this fixture as a wide wash or tight beam. Along with a massive palette of colors to choose from, the Stryker Wash also has an independent linear white color temperature control channel that can change from 3200K to 10,000K. This allows users to color correct the illumination of different skin tones of people on stage.\n\nThe Stryker Wash has variable strobe speeds, a 3-zone control mode with macros, and a large color display that makes navigation of the fixture’s menu system for setup and DMX addressing very easy. The fixture has fast, precise pan and tilt movements, along with fine pan/tilt, allowing for precision performance.",
